title: Overcoming Imposter Syndrome
description:
Have you ever told yourself, ‘I’m inadequate and out of my league’? Or do you turn down opportunities because you think you’re not ‘qualified’? Welcome to what is known as ‘Imposter Syndrome.’ In this episode, Jordan walks through seven tips on how to overcome this limiting narrative and why these untruthful thoughts appear in the first place. Get ready to kick Imposter Syndrome to the curb and begin to knock on the doors to your destiny.
